2413 Arkanoid 2
The main class (Arkanoid) will need to store information about the size of the field where all actions will occur.
Therefore:
a) add two private fields width (width) and height (height) of type int to the Arkanoid class
b) create public getters and setters for them

Requirements:
1. A private field width of type int must be created in the Arkanoid class.
2. In the Arkanoid class, a private height field of type int must be created.
3. In the Arkanoid class, the correct getter must be created for the height field.
4. In the Arkanoid class, the correct getter must be created for the width field.
5. In the Arkanoid class, the correct setter must be created for the height field.
6. In the Arkanoid class, the correct setter must be created for the width field.